{"assetKey":"Game_AdditionalContents_AdvancedLocomotionV4_CharacterAssets_MannequinSkeleton_ALS_AnimBP","graph":"CalculateStrideBlend","nodeGuid":"B486482C42B2BFC8C58A84A03B4B6A36","class":"EdGraphNode_Comment","title":"Calculate the Stride Blend. This value is used within the blendspaces to scale the stride (distance feet travel) so that the character can walk or run at different movement speeds. It also allows the walk or run gait animations to blend independently while still matching the animation speed to the movement speed, preventing the character from needing to play a half walk+half run blend. The curves are used to map the stride amount to the speed for maximum control.","comment":"Calculate the Stride Blend. This value is used within the blendspaces to scale the stride (distance feet travel) so that the character can walk or run at different movement speeds. It also allows the walk or run gait animations to blend independently while still matching the animation speed to the movement speed, preventing the character from needing to play a half walk+half run blend. The curves are used to map the stride amount to the speed for maximum control.","x":0,"y":0,"memberName":"","functionName":"","variableName":"","targetClass":"","isPure":false,"pins":[],"terms":["EdGraphNode_Comment"]}
